# Performance mods for Fabric 1.20.1

## Highly recommended list

These mods are the most highly tested, stable, and performant mods out there. We recommend adding **all** of these (or relevant alternatives) to modpacks, unless in the extremely rare cases of incompatibilities or issues. In cases of mod issues, report them to the relevant parties' issue tracker.

| Name                                                                                                   | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                | Additional Notes                                                                                                                         | Alternatives                                                              |
| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| [Alternate Current](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/alternate-current)                    | Vanilla-compatible redstone optimizations                                                                                                                                                                                  | -                                                                                                                                        | -                                                                         |
| [Bobby](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/bobby)                                            | Allows for render distances greater than the server's view-distance setting                                                                                                                                                | -                                                                                                                                        | -                                                                         |
| [Connectivity](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/connectivity)                              | Fix Login timeouts, Packet sizes errors, Payloads errors, ghostblocks and more                                                                                                                                             | -                                                                                                                                        | [Packet Fixer](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/packet-fixer) |
| [Crash Assistant](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/crash-assistant)                        | Shows a GUI after Minecraft crashes, immediately showing and analyzing all affected logs.                                                                                                                                  | Does not improve game performance by itself - instead helps diagnose issues when they do happen                                          | -                                                                         |
| [Cyanide](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cyanide)                                        | Reduces data pack world generation pain by providing useful, informative error messages.                                                                                                                                   | Does not improve game performance by itself - instead changes worldgen crash logs to be more readable                                    | -                                                                         |
| [Dynamic FPS](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dynamic-fps)                                | Improve performance when Minecraft is in the background                                                                                                                                                                    | -                                                                                                                                        | [FPS Reducer](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fps-reducer)   |
| [Fast Noise](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/zfastnoise)                                  | Optimizes worldgen speeds                                                                                                                                                                                                  | -                                                                                                                                        | -                                                                         |
| [FerriteCore](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ferritecore)                                | Memory usage optimizations                                                                                                                                                                                                 | -                                                                                                                                        | -                                                                         |
| [ImmediatelyFast](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/immediatelyfast)                        | Speeds up immediate mode rendering in Minecraft                                                                                                                                                                            | -                                                                                                                                        | -                                                                         |
| [Lithium](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/lithium)                                        | An optimization mod for Minecraft which improves server performance significantly.                                                                                                                                         | -                                                                                                                                        |                                                                           |
| [Load My Fucking Tags](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/lmft)                              | Prevents Incorrect Tag Entries from breaking an entire Tag                                                                                                                                                                 | Does not improve game performance by itself - instead attempts to resolve issues caused by mods having incorrectly formatted tag entries | -                                                                         |
| [Log Begone](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/log-begone)                                  | Allows you to stop entries from being logged in game console through phrases or regex                                                                                                                                      | -                                                                                                                                        | -                                                                         |
| [Max Health Fix](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/max-health-fix)                          | Fixes a bug with max health in Minecraft                                                                                                                                                                                   |                                                                                                                                          | -                                                                         |
| [Modernfix](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/modernfix)                                    | All-in-one mod that improves performance, reduces memory usage, and fixes many bugs                                                                                                                                        | Enabling [Dynamic Resources](https://github.com/embeddedt/ModernFix/wiki/Dynamic-Resources-FAQ) can halve RAM usage                      | -                                                                         |
| [ServerCore](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/servercore)                                  | Several patches & optimizations to improve performance and reduce lag spikes                                                                                                                                               | Highly configurable                                                                                                                      | -                                                                         |
| [Sodium](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/sodium)                                          | Rendering Optimizations                                                                                                                                                                                                    | -                                                                                                                                        | [Embeddium](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/embeddium)       |
| [Spark](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/spark)                                            | Performance profiler for Minecraft clients, servers and proxies                                                                                                                                                            | Does not improve game performance by itself - instead is a profiling tool to help diagnose performance issues                            | -                                                                         |
| [Structure Essentials](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/structure-essentials-forge-fabric) | Essential features for structures: Faster locating, distance adjustments, nearby structure command, automatic structure biome compat, structure overlap prevention, random source crash prevention, debug logging and more | -                                                                                                                                        | -                                                                         |
| [Too Fast](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/too-fast)                                      | Removes the server-side limitations on player speed that result in "player XYZ moved too fast" messages in the console and rubber-banding.                                                                                 | -                                                                                                                                        | -                                                                         |
